This was a very tasty dish. I only had one lemon but next time will use two. Maybe the other viewers that thought the lemons were to bitter cooked them too much, just cook until they start to golden. My two year old even enjoyed it. I also served it on a bed of sauteed spinach and a side of rice pilaf.

