Rating: 3
I made this the other night and it came out well. Flavorful and yummy. Everyone loved it. I served this w/ pasta and tomato sauce on the side. It's quite rich if prepared as described. When I make it again, I will cut down on the amount of oil used to fry the chicken (from 5 Tb to 3-4 Tb). Also, the amount of stock they suggest takes forever to reduce. I'd use 1c instead. I'd also add a little less butter at the end.

Rating: 3
